cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.DB, cs.AI 

This paper focuses on the extraction of metaknowledge from multimedia datasets and clustering for predictive analysis. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also involves information retrieval (IR) techniques to extract features from the data, which suggests cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as another likely sub-category. The use of clustering algorithms falls under the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning), which is also relevant to this paper. Additionally, the paper involves optimization of data representation, which is related to database (cs.DB) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories.
